{"tid":1268701,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇fb 同nflx 睇報","createTime":"2019-06-30T10:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T20:50:17.000Z","uid":226154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9dcf18c7c023cb07871d932f7f20f55b05bdbedf","tid":1268701,"uid":226154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"Netflix 同facebook 分別喺7月17同7月26 after maket 發表財報，唔知ching 點睇呢？<br />\n我個人分拆如下：<br />\n<br />\nNetflix 呢一年真係受到好大挑戰，一來有幾間公司崛起做網絡電視（apple 同迪士尼），而且迪士尼仲收返Netflix d 熱播劇，二來Netflix 收費用户逐漸飽和，而且宜家仲可以一個帳號多個手機使用，再者Netflix 冇廣告收入令我覺得佢今季好似冇咩突破，個人唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而facebook 上季比市場預期差，雖然facebook 好似冇咁多人用，但佢廣告收入仍然好理想，而且但佢旗下既ig 收入都一季比一季高，加上今季有libra虛擬貨幣既炒作，相信市場大部份投資者都睇好facebook 前景<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up 想同大家討論下，畢竟街外錢大家一齊賺"},{"pid":"719c1673eeff55bd827bf0df570affb57e30015e","tid":1268701,"uid":246729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920f3d35e0594fd772944bb7964cd09faee5103f","tid":1268701,"uid":226154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"719c1673eeff55bd827bf0df570affb57e30015e","tid":1268701,"uid":246729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"巴打你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22a645143481fc0d0d2793ef4dffb26b65cb1e2","tid":1268701,"uid":246729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"920f3d35e0594fd772944bb7964cd09faee5103f","tid":1268701,"uid":226154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"719c1673eeff55bd827bf0df570affb57e30015e","tid":1268701,"uid":246729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"巴打你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"um....美股數簿無乜心機睇, 依家望住Q4 個power point slide <br />\n一路望 一路回post<br />\n可能會有啲粗梳<br />\n佢張users 分成四prt, 美加/歐/亞太/其他<br />\n以人數計MAU DAU都係 亞太&amp;其他 佔大多數, 而增長亦都以依兩個區為主<br />\n但神奇地 revenue 仍然以歐美加佔大部份<br />\n當中嘅原因要好好深究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外,成盤數計,支出增長 30925/20450 =~50%<br />\n而revenue 55838/40653 =得37%<br />\n值得留意, 係咪公司太大隻, 錢識洗唔識搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw...科技股好多時都係睇數簿嘅盲點<br />\n利申, 我買左PINS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aab0aaed944ca7b46e098dc43ecbe1e88832fff","tid":1268701,"uid":226154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f22a645143481fc0d0d2793ef4dffb26b65cb1e2","tid":1268701,"uid":246729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"920f3d35e0594fd772944bb7964cd09faee5103f","tid":1268701,"uid":226154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"719c1673eeff55bd827bf0df570affb57e30015e","tid":1268701,"uid":246729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"巴打你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"um....美股數簿無乜心機睇, 依家望住Q4 個power point slide <br />\n一路望 一路回post<br />\n可能會有啲粗梳<br />\n佢張users 分成四prt, 美加/歐/亞太/其他<br />\n以人數計MAU DAU都係 亞太&amp;其他 佔大多數, 而增長亦都以依兩個區為主<br />\n但神奇地 revenue 仍然以歐美加佔大部份<br />\n當中嘅原因要好好深究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外,成盤數計,支出增長 30925/20450 =~50%<br />\n而revenue 55838/40653 =得37%<br />\n值得留意, 係咪公司太大隻, 錢識洗唔識搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw...科技股好多時都係睇數簿嘅盲點<br />\n利申, 我買左PINS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"咁你點睇fb 同ba 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇咗一目均衡表見到fb 岩岩穿左綠雲，但盤整緊，真係好難捉摸。而且佢個虛擬貨幣有好多國家都持有觀望態度，好驚隨時跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而ba 我就估佢財報應該會幾難睇，成日都空難737航線仲要成日停飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39795124d4d326dbf5598b6ea143ff9fb27a340b","tid":1268701,"uid":246729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"咁樓主你係想討論 財表數簿 定係要FF佢地嘅未來表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後者無得睇， 齋估<br />\nFB 隻虛疑貨幣FB自己佔幾多％， 據知有29間公司一齊參與<br />\n世界各地嘅市民對依隻libra接受程度有幾多？<br />\nFB當中可以賺到幾多錢？<br />\n唔講FB， 可以諗下其實依家每個國家都有自己類似payme嘅app， 民眾會唔會轉用libra都係未知數<br />\n我諗起幾個香港嘅例子：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tap&amp;go 最後變左賓賓用嚟匯錢返鄉下, 好明顯同當初原意好大出入,但又相當地成功<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />n年前嘅電子支票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗依家都無人記得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />payme, 估唔到可以喺兩大紅資付款工具之下生存到, 仲要係數一數二受歡迎<br />\n想帶出嘅係,科技野好難估, 如果因為libra去炒fb股價, 無問題, 話到明係炒<br />\n如果係因為libra而覺得fb盈利會大升, 我覺得太早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0368493429ea2721dee9fb357b4bae72be70603d","tid":1268701,"uid":246729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"另外, 關於netflix<br />\n頭先望過下, 幾surprise 佢嘅現金流原來都好唔掂下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負嘅營運現金流, 而且過去三年嘅利息支出增加得好快, 而相應嘅負債好似無增加得咁快, 當中原因要再望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n短炒的話, 自己諗下仲有無野可以炒<br />\n依盤生意長揸的話, 我本人唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acfb746f4aae51ae3606dcf0